                            <comment id="114025" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 1 May 2015 15:18:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since this such a new platform it looks like we will be migrating to Ubuntu 15 which uses a patches 3.19 kernel. Except patches soon to support newer kernels.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
